tions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ushikariiapoccalypse.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Shikarii Apoccalypse</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Steel Warrior Contributor</span><br>  Posts: 1004<br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/8/02 1:20:02 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1783.topic&index=1>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Defiance VS Lammy!</span><hr size=1> ac is king. that's why people like the defiance over the lammy.<br>dps, whatever, it's the same exact weapon; one gives you 20 + 6sta(x) hp's; the other gives 10 AC.<br><br>i for one would take 10 more AC over 20 + 6sta(x) hp's. <p><center><img src=http://publish.hometown.aol.com/crushr85/myhomepage/shir_small.jpg></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uwandork.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Wandor K</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>/con's RED</span><br>  Posts: 302<br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/8/02 4:21:47 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1783.topic&index=2>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Defiance VS Lammy!</span><hr size=1> DPS is identical. 9/19 is 9/19 - the damage bonus for 1h weapons are are always the same when being weilded by the same level toons.<br><br>What it comes down to is 10AC or 6STA + 20HP. Most people will trade out at the rate of 1AC = 10HP.<br><br>At 